    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend or abolish Sunday trade hours",
        "additional_details": "We are one of the few countries that still practices the very short Sunday trade hours. Extending it by an additional 2-3hrs could be a boost to the economy and potentially create more jobs for those who are looking for work.",
